## Troubleshooting

### Check Status

```bash
# Overall status
kamal server details

# App status
kamal app details

# Container status
kamal app exec 'docker ps'
```

### View Logs

```bash
# App logs
kamal app logs

# Traefik logs
kamal traefik logs

# System logs
kamal app exec 'journalctl -u docker'
```

### SSH Debug

```bash
# SSH into server
kamal app exec -i bash

# Check running containers
docker ps

# Check images
docker images

# Check volumes
docker volume ls

# Inspect container
docker inspect myapp-web-latest
```

### Common Issues

```bash
# Issue: Deploy fails
# Solution: Check logs
kamal app logs

# Issue: Can't connect to server
# Solution: Verify SSH access
ssh deploy@your-server

# Issue: Old containers not stopping
# Solution: Force stop and cleanup
kamal app stop
kamal prune --all

# Issue: SSL not working
# Solution: Check Traefik logs
kamal traefik logs
```

