## Best Practices

### DO ✅

```bash
# Use environment variables for secrets
env:
  secret:
    - DATABASE_URL
    - RAILS_MASTER_KEY

# Setup proper health checks
healthcheck:
  path: /up
  interval: 10s

# Use staging environment
kamal deploy -d staging

# Monitor logs after deploy
kamal app logs --follow

# Cleanup old images regularly
kamal prune

# Use specific versions for rollback
kamal deploy --version=v1.2.3

# Keep config in version control
git add config/deploy.yml
```

### DON'T ❌

```bash
# Don't commit secrets
# Add .env to .gitignore

# Don't skip healthchecks
# Always configure healthcheck endpoint

# Don't deploy without testing
# Test in staging first

# Don't ignore failed deployments
# Check logs and fix issues

# Don't accumulate old images
# Run kamal prune regularly
```

