## Deployment Checklist

```bash
# Before first deploy:
☐ Configure servers in deploy.yml
☐ Setup SSH keys
☐ Set environment variables
☐ Configure database
☐ Setup SSL/domain
☐ Run kamal setup

# Before each deploy:
☐ Run tests locally (rails test)
☐ Check staging deploy works
☐ Backup database
☐ Review changes
☐ Deploy: kamal deploy
☐ Monitor logs
☐ Verify application works
☐ Check health endpoint

# After deploy:
☐ Test critical features
☐ Check error tracking
☐ Monitor performance
☐ Update documentation
```

